title: Surrounded By The Most High | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Surrounded By The Most High | Joel Osteen
description:
You may be surrounded by difficulties, but the Most High God is surrounding you. The forces that are for you are greater than the forces that are against you! 


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
